      <hedline>
        <hl1>Not My Idea, Really</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Director Michael Blakemore letter on Robin Pogrebin's May 21 article holds idea of screenplay-within-a-play structure of musical City of Angels was not his idea but was part of Larry Gelbart's book (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>In Robin Pogrebin's generous piece about me [''A Director Who 'Makes It Seem Easy,' '' May 21], I seem to give the impression that the screenplay-within-a-play structure of the musical ''City of Angels'' was my idea. This, of course, is not the case. It was always part of Larry Gelbart's brilliant book.</p>
        <p>MICHAEL BLAKEMORE  London</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
